OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775426988
OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued a weather
OL,7,Fwarning for Wales as Storm Dave is
OL,8,Fexpected to hit the UK this Easter
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FA yellow weather warning for wind has
OL,12,Fbeen issued for a large part of the
OL,13,Fcountry with gales of up to 80mph
OL,14,Fexpected in some areas.
OL,16,FThe warning is in place from 5pm on
OL,17,FSaturday April 4 to 7am on Sunday
OL,18,FApril 5. Storm Dave is the Met
OL,19,FOffice's fourth named storm of the
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
