OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775426988
OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,FThe full warning from the forecaster
OL,7,Freads: "A rapidly deepening area of
OL,8,Flow pressure, Storm Dave, will cross
OL,9,FScotland on Saturday night before
OL,10,Fclearing into the North Sea on Sunday.
OL,11,FWhilst some uncertainty remains in the
OL,12,Fexact track and shape of Storm Dave, a
OL,13,Fspell of strong southwesterly winds is
OL,14,Fexpected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
