PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775426988
OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,F"Gusts of 50-60 mph are expected
OL,7,Ffairly widely with 60-70 mph in more
OL,8,Fexposed locations. The strongest winds
OL,9,Fare expected during Saturday evening
OL,10,Fwhere there is a small chance of gusts
OL,11,Fof 70-80 mph briefly, particularly
OL,12,Fnorthern England and southern
OL,13,FScotland. Large waves may lead to some
OL,14,Fdangerous conditions around windward
OL,15,Fcoasts."
OL,17,FIn Wales the warning covers
OL,18,FCeredigion, Conwy, Denbighshire,
OL,19,FFlintshire, Gwynedd, Anglesey,
OL,20,FPembrokeshire and Powys.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
