PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775426988
OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,FAccording to the Met Office, the
OL,7,Fwarning could see some roads and
OL,8,Fbridges close in the areas impacted by
OL,9,Fthe warning as well as disruptions to
OL,10,Fpublic transport.
OL,12,FIt added that power cuts may occur and
OL,13,Fsome damage to buildings could also be
OL,14,Fpossible. The Met Office also warned
OL,15,Fthere could be injuries or danger to
OL,16,Flife from flying debris.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
