OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1775426988
OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,FWith heavy traffic expected over the
OL,7,Fbank holiday weekend, RAC spokesperson
OL,8,FRod Dennis said: "The arrival of Storm
OL,9,FDave is set to make driving conditions
OL,10,Facross the north and west of the UK
OL,11,Fthis Easter particularly challenging.
OL,12,FWhile we expect leisure traffic
OL,13,Fvolumes to be slightly lower on
OL,14,FSaturday and Sunday compared with the
OL,15,Frest of the bank holiday, there will
OL,16,Fstill be millions of people on the
OL,17,Froads visiting friends and family.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
