OL,3,CMet Office issues weather warning for
OL,4,CWales as Storm Dave expected
OL,6,F"Drivers shouldn't underestimate the
OL,7,Fimpact of the very strong winds that
OL,8,Fare forecast. We recommend taking
OL,9,Fextra care on exposed, higher routes
OL,10,Fand being especially cautious when
OL,11,Fovertaking highsided vehicles, as the
OL,12,Fbuffeting effect can catch some people
OL,13,Fout. Slowing down and keeping a firm
OL,14,Fgrip on the steering wheel are both
OL,15,Fvital in these conditions."
OL,26,@wD@[O]
